    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Either configure <a href=\"http://maven.apache.org/surefire/maven-surefire-plugin/test-mojo.html#testFailureIgnore\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Surefire</a> with <code>&lt;testFailureIgnore&gt;true&lt;/testFailureIgnore&gt;</code>.</p>\n<p>Or on the command line:</p>\n<pre><code>mvn install -Dmaven.test.failure.ignore=true\n</code></pre>\n"
