    "question_id" : 4174696,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>Try to add the following configuration for surefire plugin in your pom.xml of <strong>root project</strong>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;project&gt;\n  [...]\n  &lt;build&gt;\n    &lt;plugins&gt;\n      &lt;plugin&gt;\n        &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;/groupId&gt;\n        &lt;artifactId&gt;maven-surefire-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n        &lt;configuration&gt;\n          &lt;testFailureIgnore&gt;true&lt;/testFailureIgnore&gt;\n        &lt;/configuration&gt;\n      &lt;/plugin&gt;\n    &lt;/plugins&gt;\n  &lt;/build&gt;\n  [...]\n&lt;/project&gt;\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
