  "title" : "Making Maven run all tests, even when some fail",
  "body" : "<p>I have a project with several modules. When all tests pass, Maven test runs them all.</p>\n<p>When tests fail in the first module, maven will not continue to the next project. I have testFailureIgnore set to true in Surefire settings, but it doesn't help.</p>\n<p>How do I make maven run all tests regardless of earlier failures?</p>\n"
